snippet.title: Avani: The Primal Land | Devlog
snippet.description:
This is the first devlog for Avani showing my daily schedule for a few days while I work on Avani. Avani is released here https://powerofcreation.itch.io/avani-the-primal-land and can be played for free. The development of Avani started two years back on February 25th of 2019 and I have been working on it the whole time. It started when I was still doing an apprenticeship and now I'm studying Computer Science and I have much less time than I used to have, but I'm still working hard every day to bring Avani forward.

------------------------------------------------------------
Music: Dreams - Bensound
https://www.bensound.com​
https://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music/track/dreams-chill-out
